            <li>Garantia de 7 dias</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://pay.hotmart.com/O105349552T?off=j6oa11xk" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-pulse">Assinar agora</a>
        </article>

        <article class="sales-plan-card">
          <p class="plan-badge plan-badge-save">Economize 17%</p>
          <h3>Anual</h3>
          <p class="plan-price">R$ 397,00<span class="plan-period">/ano</span></p>
          <p class="plan-payment">Equivale a R$ 33,08/mês</p>
          <ul class="plan-features">
            <li>Tudo do plano mensal</li>
            <li>Economia de R$ 82,64 no ano</li>
            <li>Acesso garantido por 12 meses</li>
